name: Inline
doclayout: true
description:
  Inline items should be spaced out consistently with right margin directional flow.
  When there is a component that involves a group of inline items there should be additional CSS written
  in that component on the :last-child CSS pseudo-class to remove the right margin on the last item in the group.
  Wrapping inline items should make use of the Stack space settings.
order: 5
